'''Longbows''' can fire [[arrows]] at targets from a further distance than [[Shortbow (weapon)|shortbows]] can, but they fire at a slower rate. They have exactly the same stats as the shortbow, but cost more due to their greater [[attack range]]. They are not used often due to their slow speed, but are sometimes used to snipe enemies from a far distance. It is commonly used by archers who need to snipe their enemies (e.g. sniping a [[lesser demon]] while camping behind a barricade far away) and can hit up to ten squares away.

